OL,3,CLawrie Hooper resigns as Isle of Man
OL,4,Chealth minister
OL,6,FResponding to the announcement, Mr
OL,7,FCannan thanked the former health
OL,8,Fminister for his work, but added
OL,9,F'there are significant challenges
OL,10,Faround ensuring financial discipline
OL,11,Fand managing the growing demand for
OL,12,Fhealth and social care services'.
OL,14,FIt comes after a predicted #16.8m
OL,15,Foverspend within healthcare, leading
OL,16,Fto a number of cuts to services at
OL,17,FManx Care.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
