OL,3,CLawrie Hooper resigns as Isle of Man
OL,4,Chealth minister
OL,6,FHowever, Mr Hooper claimed Manx Care
OL,7,Fwas being significantly 'underfunded'
OL,8,Fand he could not continue to serve a
OL,9,Fchief minister who "set out to both
OL,10,Fpublicly and privately undermine my
OL,11,Fability to do the job that is requird".
OL,13,FWithin his resignation statement, Mr
OL,14,FHooper said: "It has become
OL,15,Fincreasingly clear to me that the
OL,16,Fchief minister does not welcome my
OL,17,Fviews and is not willing to listen to
OL,18,Fthe evidence presented to him, and
OL,19,Fthat his views and mine over the
OL,20,Ffuture of the NHS are becoming
OL,21,Fincreasingly diverged.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
