OL,3,CLawrie Hooper resigns as Isle of Man
OL,4,Chealth minister
OL,6,F"I am now convinced that his ultimate
OL,7,Faim is to try and privatise our health
OL,8,Fservice, and that is not something I
OL,9,Fam able to support."
OL,11,FResponding to this claim, Mr Cannan
OL,12,Fsaid it was 'abundantly clear' that
OL,13,Fthe difference between Mr Hooper's
OL,14,F'ideology' and the 'reality Manx Care
OL,15,Ffinds itself in' was a 'bridge too far
OL,16,Ffor him'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
