OL,6,FMr Cannan denied having any intention
OL,7,Fto privatise the island's health
OL,8,Fservice, however he said further
OL,9,F'strategic action' was needed, as
OL,10,Foverspending was 'destabilising'
OL,11,Fgovernment finances.
OL,13,FThe Chair of Manx Care, Dr Wendy Reid,
OL,14,Fand CEO, Teresa Cope issued a
OL,15,Fstatement thanking Mr Hooper.
OL,17,FThey said: "Manx Care would like to
OL,18,Fexpress thanks to Minister Hooper for
OL,19,Fhis support, wise guidance and
OL,20,Fchallenge during the inception and
OL,21,Fearly years of our development.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
