OL,3,CLawrie Hooper resigns as Isle of Man
OL,4,Chealth minister
OL,6,F"We have valued his insight and
OL,7,Fclarity on many issues and wish him
OL,8,Fwell for the future. Manx Care will
OL,9,Fcontinue to strive for the best
OL,10,Fquality health and care possible for
OL,11,Fthe people of the Isle of Man while
OL,12,Fdelivering value for money.
OL,14,F"We look forward to working with the
OL,15,Fnew Minister and team."
OL,17,FMr Cannan will take over as the
OL,18,FMinister for Health and Social Care in
OL,19,Fan interim position, until he appoints
OL,20,Fa successor.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
