OL,6,FMr Hooper concluded: "I apologise to
OL,7,Fthe people of this Island for not
OL,8,Fbeing able to change this government's
OL,9,Fcourse from within.
OL,11,F"Resignation is the only card I have
OL,12,Fleft to play."
